      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAGIC BANDIT (7) shapes well for this after a lightning last start success, getting around this track over 520m in 29.39. Has the ability and looks hard to top. FOREIGN CAPITAL (2) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (29.47) at this track over 520m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Leading chance. SAMMY ETHAN (8) turned in a moderate run last time when seventh at this track over 520m behind MAGIC BANDIT (30.07) in a NG. Was a winner prior to that. Goes well out of this box with a win and six minor placings. Has ability and can atone. TAW GALAXY (3) has been in the money at his last two runs, most recently when third (29.63) in a NG over 520m at this track.",
